《帝国反击战》1980年5月6日在伦敦[[自治领剧院|自治领剧院]]首映<ref name="Rinzler-2010" />{{rp|328}}，17日在哥伦比亚特区[[约翰·肯尼迪表演艺术中心|肯尼迪中心]]办首映式，主要演员、包括[[國際特殊奧林匹克組織|特殊奥运选手]]等六百名儿童出席<ref>{{cite web | last = Kornheiser | first = Tony | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1980/05/19/the-empire-strikes-back/02fcd9c0-4abf-4f69-9ab3-a7228c669e40/ | title = The Empire Strikes Back | access-date = 2022-01-26 | website = The Washington Post | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210422131543/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1980/05/19/the-empire-strikes-back/02fcd9c0-4abf-4f69-9ab3-a7228c669e40/ | archive-date = 2021-04-22 | date = 1980-05-19 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Rinzler-2010" />{{rp|328}}。5月20日电影在伦敦[[萊斯特廣場奧迪安電影院|欧狄恩莱斯特广场]]举行全球首映式，活动号称“帝国节”，演员扮成风暴兵在全城各地与市民互动<ref name="StarWarsUKPremiere">{{cite web | first = Pete | last = Vilmur | url = https://www.starwars.com/news/an-empire-day-to-remember | title = An 'Empire Day' to remember | date = 2014-11-17 | website = StarWars.com | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210725231634/https://www.starwars.com/news/an-empire-day-to-remember | archive-date = 2021-07-25 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://gettyimagesgallery.com/images/the-empire-strikes-back-premiere/ | title = The Empire Strikes Back premiere | date = 2019-10-24 | publisher = [[盖帝图像|Getty Images]] | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211015211400/https://gettyimagesgallery.com/images/the-empire-strikes-back-premiere/ | archive-date = 2021-10-15 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Rinzler-2010" />{{rp|328}}。

电影5月21日在北美洲126家院线上映，迎接[[亡兵紀念日|亡兵紀念日]]长假周末<ref name="BOMEmpire">{{cite web | title = Star Wars: Episode V – The Empire Strikes Back (Domestic Weekend) | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211030110035/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2775811585/weekend/?ref_=bo_rl_tab#tabs | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2775811585/weekend/?ref_=bo_rl_tab#tabs | publisher = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | archive-date = 2021-10-30 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。发行商有意限制上映院线数量，大搞饥饿营销，通常只有预计口碑良好、想靠口耳相传推广的电影才会采取如此战术<ref name="NYT19800601" />。影片上映当天收入130万美元，平均每家院线10581美元<ref name="BOMEmpireOpeningDay">{{cite web | title = 1980 worldwide box office | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2775811585/?ref_=bo_rl_tab#tabs | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211015175427/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2775811585/?ref_=bo_rl_tab | archive-date = 2021-10-15 | publisher = Box Office Mojo | access-date = 2022-01-26 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，周末进账490万美元，加上周一（亡兵纪念日）150万共640万美元，平均每家电影院50919美元，远超同样新上映的竞争对手《[[滑稽秀_(电影)|滑稽秀]]》（150万美元）和《闪灵》（60万美元）登顶周末票房榜<ref name="BOMEmpire" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Domestic 1980 weekend 21 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210827120404/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1980W21/occasion/us_memorialday_weekend/ | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1980W21/occasion/us_memorialday_weekend/ | publisher = Box Office Mojo | archive-date = 2021-08-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Germain | last = Lussier | title = The movies that had the hubris to open the same week as the ''Star Wars'' films | access-date = 2022-01-26 | dead-url = no | url = https://gizmodo.com/the-movies-that-had-the-hubris-to-open-the-same-week-as-1820890662 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210903124016/https://gizmodo.com/the-movies-that-had-the-hubris-to-open-the-same-week-as-1820890662 | website = [[Gizmodo|Gizmodo]] | date = 2017-12-14 | archive-date = 2021-09-03}}</ref>。电影上映首周共收入960万美元，比《星球大战》高六成，平均每家院线76201，创下上百家电影院的新纪录<ref name="NYT19800601" /><ref>{{cite web | last = Harmetz | first = Aljean | date = 1981-06-02 | title = How does Hollywood decide if a film is a hit? | website = The New York Times | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211029071737/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/06/02/movies/how-does-hollywood-decide-if-a-film-is-a-hit.html | archive-date = 2021-10-29 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/06/02/movies/how-does-hollywood-decide-if-a-film-is-a-hit.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = ''Star Wars: Episode IV – A New Hope'' | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2759034369/weekend/?ref_=bo_tt_gr#table | publisher = Box Office Mojo | date = 2020-01-09 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211015190311/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2759034369/weekend/?ref_=bo_tt_gr | archive-date = 2021-10-15 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

《帝国反击战》两连庄后在第四个周末以360万美元跌至第三，落后西部片《[[不屈不挠_(电影)|不屈不挠]]》（370万美元）和喜剧片《[[天命_(电影)|天命]]》（362万美元）<ref name="BOMEmpireOpeningDay" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Domestic 1980 weekend 24 | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1980W24/?ref_=bo_rl_table_4 | publisher = Box Office Mojo | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-date = 2021-10-16 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211016063136/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1980W24/?ref_=bo_rl_table_4}}</ref>。上映院线增至823家后本片在第五个周末以1080万美元再度登顶<ref name="BOMEmpireOpeningDay" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Domestic 1980 weekend 25 | archive-date = 2021-10-30 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1980W25/?ref_=bo_rl_table_5 | publisher = Box Office Mojo | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211030191652/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1980W25/?ref_=bo_rl_table_5 | access-date = 2022-01-26}}</ref>。加上工作日收入，《帝国反击战》以近两千万美元刷新周票房纪录，一年后才被《[[超人II|超人II]]》以2400万美元超越<ref>{{cite web | title = Domestic 1980 week 25 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekly/1980W25/?ref_=bo_rl_table_3 | publisher = Box Office Mojo | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211015211156/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekly/1980W25/?ref_=bo_rl_table_3 | archive-date = 2021-10-15 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Harmetz | first = Aljean | date = 1981-01-30 | title = 'Superman' breaks record | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1981/06/30/movies/superman-breaks-record.html | website = The New York Times | access-date = 2022-01-26 | page = C5 | archive-date = 2021-08-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210801035610/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/06/30/movies/superman-breaks-record.html | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine | magazine = Daily Variety | title = Smokey 2 No. 1 in Domestic B.O. Maiden Wk. With $17,805,900 | date = 1980-08-25 | location = Los Angeles}}</ref>。电影此后连续七周卫冕，上映第13周以430万美元位居第二，落后新上映的《[[横冲直撞斗飞车2|横冲直撞斗飞车2]]》（1090万美元）。《帝国反击战》的院线发行周期长达32周，最多在1278家影院上映，后期票房数据已不可考。<ref name="BOMEmpireOpeningDay" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Domestic 1980 weekend 33 | publisher = Box Office Mojo | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1980W33/?ref_=bo_rl_table_13 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211030191705/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1980W33/?ref_=bo_rl_table_13 | archive-date = 2021-10-30 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

电影以约1.81至2.09亿美元高居[[1980年电影|年度票房榜首]]，遥遥领先热门喜剧片《[[朝九晚五_(1980年電影)|朝九晚五]]》（1..03亿美元）、《[[油腔滑调_(电影)|油腔滑调]]》（1.01亿美元）、《[[空前绝后满天飞|空前绝后满天飞]]》（8350万美元）<ref name="NYTimesMostPopular" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Domestic Box Office for 1980 | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/year/1980/?grossesOption=totalGrosses | publisher = Box Office Mojo | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210420204449/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/year/1980/?grossesOption=totalGrosses | archive-date = 2021-04-20 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Variety19990517">{{cite magazine | title = Box Office News | magazine = Variety | location = Los Angeles | volume = 375 | issue = 1 | date = 1999-05-17 | url = https://link.gale.com/apps/doc/A54701224/ITOF?u=wikipedia&sid=ITOF&xid=767a73b0 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | page = 30}}</ref>。虽说不及前作，但绝对是热卖之作，业界专家估算影片为制片方带来1.2亿美元收入<ref name="NYTimesIndulgent" /><ref name="NYTimesMostPopular" /><ref name="Variety19990517" />。卢卡斯收回投资并清偿债务<ref name="Rinzler-2010" />{{rp|336}}，还向雇员发放五百万美元分红<ref name="Hearn-2005" />{{rp|132}}。本片1980年在北美洲以外国家和地区上映的票房收入缺乏文献记载，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》发文称电影在英国和日本热卖，《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》称影片海外总票房1.92亿美元，加上美国和加拿大共计4.01亿美元{{refn|group="注"|相当于{{Inflation/year|US}}年的{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|401500000|1980}}}}美元。}}，高居1980年电影首位<ref name="Groves-1997" /><ref name="Woods-1997" /><ref name="NYT19800524" />。不过，《帝国反击战》没能获得前作反复上映的优待，卢卡斯认为这主要是因为续集的开放式结局<ref name="NYTimesIndulgent" /><ref name="Rinzler-2010" />{{rp|346,348}}。

《帝国反击战》此后多次重新进入院线，其中1981年7月收入2680万美元，1982年11月进账1450万美元，1997年2月经卢卡斯修改的特别版收入6760万美元<ref name="Variety19990517" />。电影的北美票房总额由此升至2.9至2.92亿美元<ref name="Variety19990517" /><ref>{{cite web | url = https://deadline.com/2020/07/star-wars-empire-strikes-back-tops-weekend-box-office-drive-ins-coronavirus-1202983364/ | title = 'Empire Strikes Back' leads at the weekend box office with $644K, 23 years after sequel's special edition – update | first = Anthony | last = D'Alessandro | date = 2020-07-13 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | website = Deadline Hollywood | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220123201258/https://deadline.com/2020/07/star-wars-empire-strikes-back-tops-weekend-box-office-drive-ins-coronavirus-1202983364/ | archive-date = 2022-01-23 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="BoMWorldwideTotal2021" /><ref name="TheNumbersWWTotal2021" />，估计全球票房达5.38至5.49亿美元<ref name="BoMWorldwideTotal2021" /><ref name="TheNumbersWWTotal2021" />。计入通货膨胀后，本片的北美票房位居[[美國和加拿大最高電影票房收入列表|影史第十三]]<ref>{{cite web | title = Top lifetime adjusted grosses | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/chart/top_lifetime_gross_adjusted/?adjust_gross_to=2020 | publisher = Box Office Mojo | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211121000650/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/chart/top_lifetime_gross_adjusted/?adjust_gross_to=2020 | archive-date = 2021-11-21 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
=== 专业评价 ===
与广受好评的前作不同，《帝国反击战》上映之初反响不一<ref name="NYTimesIndulgent" /><ref name="Rinzler-2010" />{{rp|332}}<ref>{{cite web | title = Critical Opinion: ''The Empire Strikes Back''{{'s}} original reviews | url = https://www.starwars.com/news/critical-opinion-the-empire-strikes-back-original-reviews | website = Star Wars | date = 2014-01-23 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-date = 2021-11-25 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211125193843/https://www.starwars.com/news/critical-opinion-the-empire-strikes-back-original-reviews}}</ref>，在24位影评人的年度十大佳片榜单最高排第四<ref name="Rinzler-2010" />{{rp|346}}。影迷观感不一，主要关注续集与原作显著的基调变更和剧情发展，特别是莉亚对韩的感情超过卢克、维达居然是卢克的父亲<ref>{{cite web | last = Burwick | first = Kevin | title = Star Wars fans hated Empire Strikes Back when it was first released, too | url = https://movieweb.com/empire-strikes-back-last-jedi-comparisons-reviews/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210831150736/https://movieweb.com/empire-strikes-back-last-jedi-comparisons-reviews/ | archive-date = 2021-08-31 | website = MovieWeb | date = 2017-12-23 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Taylor | first = Chris | title = 'Last Jedi' haters are nothing new. Plenty of fans hated 'Empire Strikes Back' too | url = https://mashable.com/article/last-jedi-empire-strikes-back-haters | website = [[Mashable|Mashable]] | date = 2017-12-19 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211013151854/https://mashable.com/article/last-jedi-empire-strikes-back-haters | archive-date = 2021-10-13 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

影评人认为续作是好电影但没《星球大战》好看<ref name="ReviewCanby">{{cite web | first = Vincent | last = Canby | title = 'The Empire Strikes Back' strikes a bland note | url = https://archive.nytimes.com/www.nytimes.com/library/film/061580empire.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1981-06-15 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211213024926/https://archive.nytimes.com/www.nytimes.com/library/film/061580empire.html | archive-date = 2021-12-13 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="ReviewTHR">{{cite web | first = Arthur | last = Knight | title = 'Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back': THR's 1980 review | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/empire-strikes-back-review-1980-movie-752672/ | website = [[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date = 2014-11-28 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110223653/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/empire-strikes-back-review-1980-movie-752672/ | archive-date = 2022-01-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="RevWSJ">{{cite web | first = Joy | last = Gould Boyum | title = The Empire Strikes Back | url = https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB111653069458538291 | website = [[华尔街日报|The Wall Street Journal]] | date = 1980-05-27 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110223656/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB111653069458538291 | archive-date = 2022-01-10 | dead-url = no}}{{Subscription required}}</ref>，觉得《帝国反击战》基调变得黑暗，剧情走向成熟，但风趣中冒着傻气的原作更有魅力<ref name="ReviewCanby" /><ref name="RevWSJ" /><ref name="Denby-1980">{{cite magazine | first = David | last = Denby | title = 'Star Wars' Strikes Back | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=vOUCAAAAMBAJ&q=New+York+Magazine+David+Denby+Star+Wars+67+George+Lucas&pg=PA67&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=snippet&q=New%20York%20Magazine%20David%20Denby%20Star%20Wars%2067%20George%20Lucas&f=false | date = 1980-05-26 | magazine = [[紐約客|The New Yorker]] | access-date = 2022-01-26 | dead-url = no | page = 67 | archive-date = 2022-04-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220414173624/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=vOUCAAAAMBAJ&q=New+York+Magazine+David+Denby+Star+Wars+67+George+Lucas&pg=PA67&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=snippet&q=New%20York%20Magazine%20David%20Denby%20Star%20Wars%2067%20George%20Lucas&f=false }}</ref>。《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》的乔伊·古尔德·博尤姆觉得为轻快的《星球大战》增加正剧权重实属“荒谬”，令作品纯真的一面受损。加里·阿诺德在《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》发文，称赞续集隐线更黑暗，叙事规模更宏大，营造更多可供探索的戏剧主线。<ref name="RevWaPoGaryArnold">{{cite web | first = Gary | last = Arnold | title = Darth Vader's surprise attack | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/review97/empirestrikesbackarnold.htm | website = The Washington Post | date = 1980-05-18 | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200623185552/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/review97/empirestrikesbackarnold.htm | archive-date = 2020-06-23 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="RevWSJ" />《[[紐約客|紐約客]]》刊登[[大卫·丹比|大卫·丹比]]的文章，宣称电影比原作更引人入胜，但在[[坎普风|坎普风]]方面尚有欠缺<ref name="Denby-1980" />。《好莱坞报道》的[[亚瑟·奈特|亚瑟·奈特]]认为原作构思新颖，结合其后面世的大量太空歌剧电影令本片颇具衍生作品意味，但《帝国反击战》仍是《星球大战》过后最优秀的太空歌剧<ref name="ReviewTHR" /><ref name="RevWaPoGaryArnold" />。杰拉尔德·克拉克在《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》发文，认为续集在多方面超越前作，视觉和艺术角度都更胜一筹<ref>{{cite web | first = Gerald | last = Clarke | title = The Empire Strikes Back! |page=3 | url = http://content.time.com/time/subscriber/article/0,33009,924122-3,00.html | date = 1980-05-19 | website = Time | access-date = 2022-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071214061850/https://time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,924122-3,00.html | archive-date = 2007-12-14 | dead-url = yes}}</ref>。《纽约时报》刊登[[文森特·坎比|文森特·坎比]]的评论，认为续集更显机械，缺乏悬念<ref name="ReviewCanby" />。

《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》刊登[[查尔斯·尚普林|查尔斯·尚普林]]的文章，认为电影悬念结局构思巧妙，完成叙事的同时又吸引观众期待下集；但克拉克觉得如此结局难令观众满意<ref name="RevLaTimes">{{cite web | first = Charles | last = Champlin | title = From the archives: In the ''Star Wars'' saga, ''Empire'' strikes forward | url = https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-in-the-star-wars-saga-empire-strikes-forward-20151202-story.html | date = 1980-05-18 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | website = Los Angeles Times | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220112130622/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-in-the-star-wars-saga-empire-strikes-forward-20151202-story.html | archive-date = 2022-01-22 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="RevTimePage5">{{cite magazine | first = Gerald | last = Clarke | title = The Empire Strikes Back! |page=5 | url = http://content.time.com/time/subscriber/article/0,33009,924122-5,00.html | date = 1980-05-19 | magazine = Time | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071113144024/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,924122-5,00.html | archive-date = 2007-11-13 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。坎比与《[[芝加哥读者|芝加哥读者]]》作家[[戴夫·科尔|戴夫·科尔]]都认为电影中场应该更注重叙事发展而非阐述，还觉得本片从头到尾情节几乎没有进展<ref name="ReviewCanby" /><ref name="RevDaveKehr">{{cite web | first = Dave | last = Kehr | url = http://onfilm.chicagoreader.com/movies/capsules/3101_EMPIRE_STRIKES_BACK | website = Chicago Reader | date =  | access-date = 2009-03-15 | title = The Empire Strikes Back | archive-date = 2009-03-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090315081601/http://onfilm.chicagoreader.com/movies/capsules/3101_EMPIRE_STRIKES_BACK | dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name="RevWSJ" />。《华盛顿邮报》专栏作家[[朱迪思·马丁|朱迪思·马丁]]把《帝国反击战》批为“垃圾好片”，缺乏独立剧情导致乍一看挺能唬人但转瞬即逝<ref>{{cite web | first = Judith | last = Martin | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/review97/empirestrikesbackmartin.htm | website = The Washington Post | date = 1980-05-23 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | title = 'The Empire Strikes Back' | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220102095609/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/review97/empirestrikesbackmartin.htm | archive-date = 2022-01-02 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。奈特与克拉克感觉剧情有时难以理解，奈特不适应第三幕的多主线切换，克拉克认为剧情节奏太快，令人应接不暇甚至错过重要内容<ref name="ReviewTHR" /><ref name="RevTimePage5" />。科尔和《[[视与听|视与听]]》写手理查德·库姆斯认为电影似乎把特效看得比人物塑造还重要，视觉奇观与动作场面对情节几乎毫无推动<ref name="RevDaveKehr" /><ref name="RevSightandSound">{{cite web | first = Richard | last = Combs | title = The Empire Strikes Back archive review: return of the gimmicks | url = https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/reviews-recommendations/empire-strikes-back-star-wars-episode-v | date = 2019-12-18 | publisher = British Film Institute | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211025200829/https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/reviews-recommendations/empire-strikes-back-star-wars-episode-v | archive-date = 2021-10-25 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

主要演员的演出同样评价不一<ref name="RevWSJ" /><ref name="RevLaTimes" /><ref name="RevDaveKehr" />。奈特称赞人物经过克什纳执导后多一分真实，少一分原型感<ref name="ReviewTHR" />。哈米尔、费雪、福特的演出赢得赞誉，尚普林称哈米尔的演绎充满“少年纯真”、令人着迷，费雪的人物塑造独立自主<ref name="ReviewTHR" /><ref name="RevLaTimes" /><ref name="RevVariety">{{cite web | first = James | last = Harwood | url = https://variety.com/1980/film/reviews/the-empire-strikes-back-1200424800/ | website = Variety | date = 1980-05-07 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | title = Review: 'The Empire Strikes Back' | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110223656/https://variety.com/1980/film/reviews/the-empire-strikes-back-1200424800/ | archive-date = 2022-01-10 }}</ref>。阿诺德认为电影人物发展不足，似乎更注重“派头”，人物基本没有变化<ref name="RevWaPoGaryArnold" />，科尔感觉失去卢卡斯指导后人物更显“僵硬”<ref name="RevDaveKehr" />。奈特觉得吉尼斯演出不够专心<ref name="ReviewTHR" />，[[珍妮特·马斯林|珍妮特·马斯林]]批评片中唯一的黑人主角兰多“夸夸其谈、不可信赖、装腔作势”<ref>{{cite web | last = Maslin | first = Janet | title = Film: Robots return in 'Empire Strikes': 'Star Wars' sequel | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1980/05/21/archives/film-robots-return-in-empire-strikesstar-wars-sequel.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1980-05-21 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211029071143/https://www.nytimes.com/1980/05/21/archives/film-robots-return-in-empire-strikesstar-wars-sequel.html | archive-date = 2021-10-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[吉恩·西斯克|吉恩·西斯克]]在《[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]》发文，认为片中以机器人、丘巴卡等非人类角色最讨喜，尤达是电影精华所在<ref>{{cite web | first = Gene | last = Siskel | title = Star Wars Episode VII | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-2005-05-20-0505200368-story.html | website = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | date = 2005-05-20 | access-date = 2022-01-10 | archive-date = 2022-01-10 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110225145/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-2005-05-20-0505200368-story.html }}</ref>。奈特、古尔德·博尤姆、阿诺德赞扬布偶人物表情真假莫辨，简直就像演员的脸已经融入布偶<ref name="ReviewTHR" /><ref name="RevWSJ" /><ref name="RevWaPoGaryArnold" />。坎比批评真人角色平淡无奇、不值一提，机器人角色提供的观影乐趣逐渐消逝，只有尤达偶尔出场时效果还不错<ref name="ReviewCanby" />。

阿诺德认可克什纳的导演功底，其他评论认为卢卡斯的监督痕迹很重，克什纳导演风格不显。丹比感觉《帝国反击战》没有克什纳的导演特点，坎比甚至认为单看电影根本不可能判断哪些部分由克什纳贡献。<ref name="ReviewCanby" /><ref name="Denby-1980" /><ref name="RevWaPoGaryArnold" />库姆斯指出，导演在本片注重人物未免不智，有损《星球大战》连续漫画式节奏<ref name="RevSightandSound" />。影评人称赞摄影师[[彼得·苏希茨基|彼得·苏希茨基]]的视觉呈现，色彩选择胆量十足<ref name="ReviewTHR" /><ref name="RevWaPoGaryArnold" />，特效“叹为观止”<ref name="RevWSJ" />、“新颖独特”<ref name="ReviewTHR" />、看上去眼花瞭乱<ref name="RevWaPoGaryArnold" />。[[吉姆·哈伍德|吉姆·哈伍德]]指出，大家的失望纯属前作太过出色，其他电影一直在效仿<ref name="RevVariety" />。尚普林认可电影没有把特效当成主角，而是用来改善观感<ref name="RevLaTimes" />。

=== 荣誉 ===
[[File:Johnwilliams2006.JPG|缩略图]]赢得两项[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]，入围[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]、[[金球獎|金球獎]]、[[英国电影和电视艺术学院|英国电影和电视艺术学院]]]]

