-hugo-awards/ | url = http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1981-hugo-awards/ | publisher = [[世界科幻大会|World Science Fiction Convention]] | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-date = 2021-12-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = People's Choice Awards | publisher = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | url = https://www.upi.com/Archives/1981/03/06/Peoples-Choice-Awards/4118352702800/ | date = 1981-03-06 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211008134553/https://www.upi.com/Archives/1981/03/06/Peoples-Choice-Awards/4118352702800/ | archive-date = 2021-10-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 后续 ==
=== 特别版及其他变更 ===
卢卡斯计划在20世纪末开发[[星際大戰前傳三部曲|前传三部曲]]，把《帝国反击战》等原版三部曲重制后起名《星球大战三部曲：特别版》发布，检验近20年来特效手段的进步。重制过程不乏变更或新增内容，有些还与前传电影关联。卢卡斯表示，特别版采用现代科技重制，与他的原始构想更相符。变更内容如片头雪地怪兽的全貌，地点、建筑、人物的[[電腦合成影像|電腦合成影像]]镜头。<ref name="WiredSPecial">{{cite web | first = Drew | last = Stewart | title = Disney+ should offer the ''Star Wars'' original cuts—all of them | access-date = 2022-01-27 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.wired.com/story/put-original-star-wars-on-disney-plus/ | website = Wired | date = 2020-03-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220121185320/https://www.wired.com/story/put-original-star-wars-on-disney-plus/ | archive-date = 2022-01-21 }}</ref>影评人对上述变更青眼有加，[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]称赞《帝国反击战》是原版三部曲最佳兼“核心之作”<ref>{{cite web | first = Roger | last = Ebert | author-link = 罗杰·埃伯特 | title = ''The Empire Strikes Back'' | url = https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-empire-strikes-back-1997 | date = 1997-02-21 | website = RogerEbert.com | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220102095453/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-empire-strikes-back-1997 | archive-date = 2022-01-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Peter | last = Stack | title = Saga's second 'strike' is its swiftest | url = https://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/Saga-s-Second-Strike-Is-Its-Swiftest-2829500.php | date = 1997-08-29 | website = [[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]] | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211015211706/https://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/Saga-s-Second-Strike-Is-Its-Swiftest-2829500.php | archive-date = 2021-10-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Lisa | last = Schwarzbaum | title = ''The Empire Strikes Back'' | url = https://ew.com/article/1997/03/07/empire-strikes-back-2/ | date = 1997-03-07 | website = Entertainment Weekly | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210830221932/https://ew.com/article/1997/03/07/empire-strikes-back-2/ | archive-date = 2021-08-30 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

特别版发布后几经变更，2004年再度发行时，《[[星際大戰六部曲：絕地大反攻|星際大戰六部曲：絕地大反攻]]》开始扮演银河皇帝的[[伊恩·麦克迪阿梅德|伊恩·麦克迪阿梅德]]取代雷维尔与贝克版<ref name="WiredSPecial" />；《[[星際大戰二部曲：複製人全面進攻|星際大戰二部曲：複製人全面進攻]]》里扮演童年克隆人费特的[[特穆拉·莫里森|特穆拉·莫里森]]为《帝国反击战》台词配音，取代维格林<ref name="VanityFairBulloch" />。2011年蓝光版也有小变更，为机器人着陆形成撞击坑新增火焰并调整颜色<ref name="WIredBlurRayReview">{{cite web | first = Jamie | last = Benning | title = Jamie Benning reviews the Star Wars Blu-ray set | url = https://www.wired.com/2011/09/jamie-benning-reviews-the-star-wars-blu-ray-set/ | website = Wired | date = 2011-09-16 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211015225128/https://www.wired.com/2011/09/jamie-benning-reviews-the-star-wars-blu-ray-set/ | archive-date = 2021-10-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Ben | last = Moore | title = 'Star Wars' Blu-ray: List of changes to the original trilogy | url = https://screenrant.com/star-wars-bluray-changes/ | website = Screen Rant | date = 2011-09-14 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211027211752/https://screenrant.com/star-wars-bluray-changes/ | archive-date = 2021-10-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。影迷对特别版看法不一，批评许多变更毫无必要或对原版改动太大<ref name="WiredSPecial" /><ref>{{cite web | website = Syfy | title = Lucasfilm defends DVD changes | access-date = 2008-10-02 | archive-date = 2008-10-02 | url = http://www.scifi.com/scifiwire/art-film.html?2004-09/09/11.30.film | date = 2004-09-09 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081002115333/http://www.scifi.com/scifiwire/art-film.html?2004-09%2F09%2F11.30.film }}</ref>。未修改的原版三部曲在2006年发布DVD后再没推出商品，该版采用20世纪90年代初的[[鐳射影碟|鐳射影碟]]录制，影迷为保护原版筹建推出“[[哈米非专业版|哈米非专业版]]”<ref>{{cite web | first = Matthew | last = Yglesias | title = This is the best version of Star Wars — and watching it is a crime | website = Variety | date = 2015-05-12 | url = https://www.vox.com/2015/1/30/7952859/despecialized-edition-download | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211220235306/https://www.vox.com/2015/1/30/7952859/despecialized-edition-download | archive-date = 2021-12-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Daniel | last = Miller | title = Restoring ''Star Wars'' | url = https://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-12-14/restoring-star-wars/6994818?nw=0&r=HtmlFragment | date = 2015-12-13 | website = [[澳大利亚广播公司|Australian Broadcasting Corporation]] | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211221000816/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-12-14/restoring-star-wars/6994818?nw=0&r=HtmlFragment | archive-date = 2021-12-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2010年纪录片《[[人人都恨乔治·卢卡斯|人人都恨乔治·卢卡斯]]》反映《星球大战》系列电影、影迷、卢卡斯之间的关系<ref name="IndependentPrequels">{{cite web | first = Clarisse | last = Loughrey | title = Why the Star Wars prequels finally deserve some respect | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/star-wars-revenge-of-the-sith-anniversary-prequels-defence-anakin-padme-a9519701.html | website = [[獨立報|The Independent]] | date = 2020-05-19 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112223539/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/star-wars-revenge-sith-anniversary-prequels-defence-anakin-padme-a9519701.html | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 家用媒体 ===
《帝国反击战》的[[家用录像系统|VHS]]录像带、激光影碟、[[电容式电视唱片|电容式电视影碟]]1985年发布，录像带和激光影碟此后多次再版，其中不乏原版三部曲套装、收藏版，并有宽屏版、音效重制版之类小调整。1992年特别收藏版包含纪录片《从星球大战到绝地归来：传奇制作》；1997年原版三部曲特别版又发布录像带。<ref name="EmpireHomeVideo">{{cite web | title = Who shot first? The complete list of Star Wars changes | author = Ben Kirby | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/star-wars-changes/ | website = Empire | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211026124815/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/star-wars-changes/ | date = 2019-11-28 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-date = 2021-10-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Collectibles from the Outer Rim: ''Star Wars'' VHS releases! | website = StarWars.com | date = 2015-11-10 | url = https://www.starwars.com/news/collectibles-from-the-outer-rim-star-wars-vhs-releases | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211203192510/https://www.starwars.com/news/collectibles-from-the-outer-rim-star-wars-vhs-releases | archive-date = 2021-12-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1987年11月《帝国反击战》在电视首播，播出前是达斯·维达以第二人称视角介绍，包装成地球播放银河帝国电视频道<ref>{{cite web | url = https://comicbook.com/starwars/amp/news/star-wars-empire-strikes-back-tv-commercial-darth-vader/ | title = 'The Empire Strikes Back' debuted on TV with this awesome Imperial interruption | last = Cavanaugh | first = Patrick | date = 2018-11-21 | website = ComicBook.com | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210518221235/https://comicbook.com/starwars/amp/news/star-wars-empire-strikes-back-tv-commercial-darth-vader/ | archive-date = 2021-05-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Steve | last = Weinstein | title = Weekend TV : Networks Offer Banquet Of Viewing Choices For Thanksgiving Week | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-11-21-ca-5412-story.html | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1987-11-21 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211221202830/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-11-21-ca-5412-story.html | archive-date = 2021-12-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

本片2004年与《星球大战》、《绝地归来》一起发行[[DVD-Video|DVD]]，三部电影均有改动，另附纪录片《[[梦之帝国：星球大战三部曲的故事|梦之帝国：星球大战三部曲的故事]]》介绍三部曲制作<ref>{{cite web | first = Bryan | last = Young | title = Star Wars weekly: Sith Troopers at SDCC and a long-lost Lucas doc | website = Syfy | access-date = 2021-05-18 | dead-url = yes | url = https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/star-wars-weekly-sith-troopers-at-sdcc-and-a-long-lost-lucas-doc | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210518214851/https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/star-wars-weekly-sith-troopers-at-sdcc-and-a-long-lost-lucas-doc | archive-date = 2021-05-18 | date = 2019-07-19 }}</ref>。卢卡斯表示修改后原三部曲更符合他的期望，不打算再将原版修复后发布，但公众需求最终促使限量DVD收藏版2006年问世，其中包含的未修改原版三部曲取自1993年权威版激光影碟，画面显示存在问题<ref name="EmpireHomeVideo" />。

《帝国反击战》特别收藏版[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]2011年发布，既有修复过的原版三部曲，又有原版、前传三部曲加电影制作花絮版<ref name="WIredBlurRayReview" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Pre-order ''Star Wars'': The complete saga on Blu-ray now! | url = http://www.starwars.com/themovies/saga/preorder_bluray/index.html | website = StarWars.com | date = 2011-01-06 | access-date = 2011-09-02 | dead-url = yes | archive-date = 2011-09-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110902020047/http://www.starwars.com/themovies/saga/preorder_bluray/index.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Jamie | last = Benning | title = The ''Star Wars'' Blu-ray set gets 3.5 out of 5 | url = https://gizmodo.com/the-star-wars-blu-ray-set-gets-3-5-out-of-5-5841183 | website = io9 | date = 2011-09-16 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210518220834/https://io9.gizmodo.com/the-star-wars-blu-ray-set-gets-3-5-out-of-5-5841183 | archive-date = 2021-05-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2015年，《帝国反击战》等电影在众多平台[[数字发行|数字发行]]，经1997年特别版胶片修复制作的[[4K解析度|4K解析度]]版2019年在[[Disney+|Disney+]]发布<ref>{{cite web | last = Vlessing | first = Etan | title = 'Star Wars' movie franchise headed to digital HD | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/star-wars-movie-franchise-headed-786673/ | access-date = 2022-01-27 | website = The Hollywood Reporter | date = 2015-04-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211117095550/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/star-wars-movie-franchise-headed-786673/ | archive-date = 2021-11-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Adrienne | last = Tyler | title = ''Star Wars'' movies are better on Disney+ (they fix Lucas changes) | archive-date = 2021-11-17 | dead-url = no | url = https://screenrant.com/star-wars-movies-disney-plus-better-fix-lucas-changes/ | website = Screen Rant | date = 2019-11-21 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211117095550/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/star-wars-movie-franchise-headed-786673/ }}</ref>。2020年27碟天行者传奇盒装包含全部九部电影，每部都有蓝光影碟、4K[[超高清蓝光光碟|超高清蓝光光碟]]共三碟，其中还有取自2011年版的特别花絮<ref>{{Cite web | last = Lussier | first = Germain | url = https://gizmodo.com/lets-dive-into-star-wars-the-skywalker-sagas-27-disc-b-1842496774 | date = 2020-03-27 | title = Let's dive into ''Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga''{{'}}s 27-disc box set | website = io9 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210817191208/https://gizmodo.com/lets-dive-into-star-wars-the-skywalker-sagas-27-disc-b-1842496774 | archive-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

