web.archive.org/web/20220122140442/https://www.businessinsider.com/empire-strikes-back-voted-greatest-movie-ever-2014-6 | archive-date = 2022-01-22 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。维达自承乃卢克之父被誉为影史绝佳[[大逆轉|大逆轉]]{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref>{{cite web | first = Eliana | last = Dockterman | title = 35 sequels that are better than the original movie | archive-date = 2021-11-09 | url = https://time.com/5353143/sequels-better-than-original/ | website = Time | date = 2018-08-30 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211109035113/https://time.com/5353143/sequels-better-than-original/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="DOGMixed" /><ref>{{cite web | first1 = Germain | last1 = Lussier | first2 = Vincent | last2 = Tremblay | first3 = Max | last3 = Jean-Louis | title = The legacy of ''Empire Strikes Back''{{'s}} biggest spoiler, 40 years later | url = https://gizmodo.com/the-legacy-of-empire-strikes-backs-biggest-spoiler-40-1843398628 | website = io9 | date = 2020-05-13 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-date = 2021-08-20 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210820031909/https://gizmodo.com/the-legacy-of-empire-strikes-backs-biggest-spoiler-40-1843398628 }}</ref><ref name="USATodayBest" /><ref>{{cite web | title = The 50 best movie and TV show twists of all time | url = https://www.theringer.com/movies/2020/10/20/21523663/movie-tv-twists-ranked-ranking | website = The Ringer | date = 2020-10-20 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-date = 2021-05-23 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210523114817/https://www.theringer.com/movies/2020/10/20/21523663/movie-tv-twists-ranked-ranking }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Justin | last = Kirkland | title = The best plot twists in movie history that we never saw coming | url = https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/movies/g34752871/best-plot-twist-movies/ | website = [[时尚先生_(刊物)|Esquire]] | date = 2020-11-27 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.arc