ite = Syfy | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210525185639/https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/the-best-star-wars-scene-is-han-and-leias-i-love-youi-know-exchange-in-empire | date = 2019-12-03 | url = https://www.syfy.com/syfy-wire/the-best-star-wars-scene-is-han-and-leias-i-love-youi-know-exchange-in-empire }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first1 = Christine | last1 = Nguyen | first2 = Neil | last2 = Janowitz | title = The story behind Han Solo's line 'I know' in ''The Empire Strikes Back'' | archive-date = 2021-05-25 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210525185644/https://www.vulture.com/2016/11/han-solo-i-know-the-empire-strikes-back.html | url = https://www.vulture.com/2016/11/han-solo-i-know-the-empire-strikes-back.html | website = [[紐約_(雜誌)|Vulture]] | date = 2016-11-16 | access-date = 2022-01-27 }}{{Subscription required}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Brian | last = Cronin | title = ''Empire Strikes Back'': Why Han Solo's 'I know' line drove Carrie Fisher crazy | url = https://www.cbr.com/star-wars-empire-strikes-back-han-solo-i-know-line-carrie-fisher-leia-crazy/ | website = Comic Book Resources | date = 2020-05-21 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211015211706/https://www.cbr.com/star-wars-empire-strikes-back-han-solo-i-know-line-carrie-fisher-leia-crazy/ | archive-date = 2021-10-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="DOGMixed" />}}。

《帝国杂志》把本片排在史上最佳续集第六位，称赞悬而未决的“大胆”结局，敢于违抗原作模式<ref>{{cite web | title = 50 greatest movie sequels | url = http://www.empireonline.com/50greatestsequels/default.asp?c=6 | website = Empire | access-date = 2015-09-23 | archive-date = 2015-09-23 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150923061111/http://www.empireonline.com/50greatestsequels/default.asp?c=6 }}</ref>。[[极客巢穴|极客巢穴]]网认为《帝国反击战》可谓卢卡斯代表作，在史上所有续集电影仅次于《[[異形2|異形2]]》；《[[花花公子|花花公子]]》把本片排在续集第三，赞扬片尾揭露卢克与维达父子关系堪称“情感核心，令《星球大战》（系列电影）飞升进入永恒现代传奇的万神殿”<ref name="DOGBlockbusterSequel" /><ref name="Playboy" />。[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]<ref>{{cite web | first = Christian | last = Blauvelt | title = The 10 greatest movie sequels of all time | url = https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20141210-the-10-greatest-movie-sequels | publisher = BBC | date = 2014-12-10 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211028133614/https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20141210-the-10-greatest-movie-sequels | archive-date = 2021-10-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[Collider|Collider]]网站都把影片评为影史续集杰作<ref name="BestSequelCollider">{{cite web | first = Robin | last = Raven | title = 30 best sequels no one saw coming | archive-date = 2021-10-15 | url = https://collider.com/galleries/best-sequels-movie-tv/ | website = Collider | date = 2019-02-25 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211015211707/https://collider.com/galleries/best-sequels-movie-tv/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，《时代杂志》与《花花公子》认为《帝国反击战》是续集超越原作的代表<ref name="Playboy" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Eliana | last = Dockterman | title = 35 sequels that are better than the original movie | url = https://time.com/5353143/sequels-better-than-original/ | website = Time | date = 2018-08-30 | access-date = 2022-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211109035113/https://time.com/5353143/sequels-better-than-original/ | archive-date = 2021-11-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。评论汇总网《[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]》根据影评综合打分把本片排在最佳续集第27位<ref>{{cite web