callbacks-easter-eggs-mcu-marvel-kevin-feige | website = IGN | date = 2019-10-01 | access-date = 2022-01-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211126102414/https://www.ign.com/articles/2019/10/01/star-wars-references-callbacks-easter-eggs-mcu-marvel-kevin-feige | archive-date = 2021-11-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、《[[太空炮弹|太空炮弹]]》、《[[大青蛙布偶秀|大青蛙布偶秀]]》、《[[特工老爹|特工老爹]]》、《[[南方公園|南方公園]]》<ref name="CultureFilm" />、《[[辛普森一家|辛普森一家]]》<ref>{{cite web | first = Adam-Troy | last = Castro | title = 10 greatest Star Wars moments from The Simpsons | dead-url = yes | url = https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/simpsons_star_wars | website = Syfy | date = 2012-12-14 | access-date = 2021-09-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210917010647/https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/simpsons_star_wars | archive-date = 2021-09-17 }}</ref>、《[[恶搞之家|恶搞之家]]》、《[[机器鸡|机器鸡]]》<ref>{{cite web | first = Alex | last = Payne | title = Family Guy: The story behind the show's Star Wars episodes | url = https://www.cbr.com/family-guy-story-behind-star-wars-episodes/ | publisher = Comic Book Resources | date = 2021-06-02 | access-date = 2022-01-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211015211353/https://www.cbr.com/family-guy-story-behind-star-wars-episodes/ | archive-date = 2021-10-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2010年，《帝国反击战》因“文化、历史和美学领域的显著成就”入选[[國會圖書館_(美國)|美国国会图书馆]][[國家影片登記表|國家影片登記表]]<ref>{{cite web | title = Hollywood blockbusters, independent films and shorts selected for 2010 national film registry | url = https://www.loc.gov/item/prn-10-273/ | publisher = [[國會圖書館_(美國)|Library of Congress]] | access-date = 2022-01-28 | date = 2010-12-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211026021116/https://www.loc.gov/item/prn-10-273/ | archive-date = 2021-10-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/empire-strikes-airplane-25-movies-65915/ | title = 'Empire Strikes Back', 'Airplane!' among 25 movies named to National Film Registry | access-d